                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Puis Rouen la gothique et l'Océan qui gronde.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Une écume d'argent brode la vague blonde,\nLa rive fuit. — Voici Mante et sa double tour,\nPuis cent autres clochers qui filent tour à tour ;\nPuis Rouen la gothique et l'Océan qui gronde."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Au dos du vieux lion, terreur des matelots,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Vous allez confier votre barque fragile,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Et flatter de la main sa crinière de flots.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Au dos du vieux lion, terreur des matelots,\nVous allez confier votre barque fragile,\nEt flatter de la main sa crinière de flots."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Horace fit une ode au vaisseau de Virgile :",
